    public class AbstractFXForm
extends javafx.scene.control.Control
    This control can be used to show a form to the user. The form handle a collection a Element.

      • getConstraintViolations

        public javafx.collections.ObservableList<javax.validation.ConstraintViolation> getConstraintViolations()
        Get an ObservableList mirroring all constraint violations in the form. This method can be used to implement some kind of validation of the form or to display all constraint violations. This list is updated each time the user inputs data that violates a constraint or fixes a violation.
        Returns:
        the ObservableList containing current constraint violations
